      <title>飞利浦第二​​大投资者在 Apnea 交易后增持股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/philips-second-biggest-investor-raises-stake-after-apnea-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在荷兰皇家飞利浦公司 (Royal Philips NV) 解决了与其有缺陷的睡眠呼吸暂停机器相关的索赔问题两个月后，第二家主要投资者增持了这家医疗科技巨头的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/philips-second-biggest-investor-raises-stake-after-apnea-deal</guid>
